cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.RO 

The paper proposes a novel multi-tasking genetic algorithm for optimization, which integrates evolutionary computation and multi-task learning. The paper also proposes a simultaneous optimization strategy for fuzzy system design. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.LG (Machine Learning), which are related to optimization and learning. The paper also involves fuzzy system design, which is related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper uses genetic algorithms, which are related to cs.RO (Robotics).
